statements: SELECT * FROM fuel_efficiency_ratings WHERE city_mpg > 30
SELECT model_name, year, city_mpg, highway_mpg FROM fuel_efficiency_ratings WHERE highway_mpg > 25
SELECT model_id, model_name FROM fuel_efficiency_ratings WHERE year = 2020
SELECT * FROM fuel_efficiency_ratings WHERE city_mpg = 28 AND highway_mpg = 36
SELECT model_id, model_name, city_mpg, highway_mpg FROM fuel_efficiency_ratings ORDER BY city_mpg DESC
SELECT model_name, city_mpg, highway_mpg FROM fuel_efficiency_ratings WHERE year < 2020 ORDER BY city_mpg DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT model_name, year, city_mpg, highway_mpg FROM fuel_efficiency_ratings WHERE city_mpg > 30 AND highway_mpg > 40 ORDER BY year ASC LIMIT 10;
SELECT model_id, model_name, year, city_mpg, highway_mpg FROM fuel_efficiency_ratings WHERE city_mpg < 20 AND highway_mpg < 30 ORDER BY model_id DESC LIMIT 3;
SELECT * FROM fuel_efficiency_ratings WHERE year >= 2015 AND city_mpg BETWEEN 25 AND 35 ORDER BY model_name ASC LIMIT 5;
SELECT model_name, city_mpg, highway_mpg FROM fuel_efficiency_ratings WHERE model_name LIKE 'Toyota%' ORDER BY city_mpg DESC, year ASC LIMIT 5;
SELECT * FROM CarModels;
SELECT model_name, manufacturer, production_year FROM CarModels WHERE fuel_type = 'Electric';
SELECT id, model_name, manufacturer, production_year, city_mpg, highway_mpg FROM CarModels WHERE manufacturer = 'Toyota';
SELECT model_name, production_year, city_mpg, highway_mpg FROM CarModels ORDER BY production_year DESC;
SELECT id, model_name, manufacturer, fuel_type, city_mpg, highway_mpg FROM CarModels WHERE city_mpg > 25 AND highway_mpg > 30;
SELECT * FROM CarModels WHERE production_year > 2010 ORDER BY model_name DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT model_name, manufacturer, fuel_type FROM CarModels WHERE fuel_type = 'Electric' ORDER BY manufacturer ASC;
SELECT model_name, city_mpg, highway_mpg FROM CarModels WHERE city_mpg > 25 AND highway_mpg > 30 ORDER BY city_mpg DESC, highway_mpg DESC;
SELECT manufacturer, production_year, COUNT(*) AS total_models FROM CarModels GROUP BY manufacturer, production_year HAVING total_models > 1 ORDER BY manufacturer ASC, production_year DESC;

SELECT cm.model_name, fe.fuel_efficiency_rating, fe.emissions_rating FROM CarModels cm INNER JOIN FuelEfficiencyRatings fe ON cm.id = fe.car_model_id WHERE fe.fuel_efficiency_rating > 30 AND fe.emissions_rating < 5 ORDER BY fe.fuel_efficiency_rating DESC, fe.emissions_rating ASC LIMIT 5;
SELECT * FROM CarModels;
SELECT model_name, manufacturer FROM CarModels ORDER BY manufacturer DESC;
SELECT model_name, fuel_capacity FROM CarDetails WHERE fuel_type = 'Petrol';
SELECT model_name, efficiency_rating FROM FuelEfficiency ORDER BY efficiency_rating ASC;
SELECT model_name, fuel_capacity, fuel_type FROM CarDetails WHERE fuel_capacity > 50 ORDER BY fuel_capacity DESC;
SELECT * FROM CarModels;
SELECT model_name, manufacturer FROM CarModels WHERE model_id = 1;
SELECT model_id, model_name, efficiency_rating FROM CarModels JOIN FuelEfficiency ON CarModels.model_id = FuelEfficiency.model_id;
SELECT CarModels.model_name, CarDetails.fuel_capacity, CarDetails.fuel_type FROM CarModels JOIN CarDetails ON CarModels.model_id = CarDetails.model_id;
SELECT model_name, manufacturer FROM CarModels WHERE manufacturer = 'Toyota';
SELECT * FROM car_models;
SELECT model_name, year FROM car_models ORDER BY year DESC;
SELECT manufacturer, model_name, year FROM car_models WHERE manufacturer = 'Toyota';
SELECT * FROM efficiency_ratings WHERE city_mpg > 30 AND highway_mpg > 25;
SELECT manufacturer_name, country FROM manufacturers ORDER BY country ASC;
SELECT * FROM car_models WHERE year > 2015;
SELECT model_name, manufacturer FROM car_models WHERE fuel_type = 'Electric';
SELECT manufacturer, model_name, year FROM car_models ORDER BY year DESC, manufacturer ASC;
SELECT c.model_name, e.city_mpg, e.highway_mpg, e.combined_mpg FROM car_models c JOIN efficiency_ratings e ON c.car_id = e.car_id;
SELECT m.manufacturer_name, COUNT(c.car_id) as total_models FROM manufacturers m JOIN car_models c ON m.manufacturer_id = c.car_id GROUP BY m.manufacturer_name;
SELECT * FROM car_models;
SELECT id, model_name, manufacturer FROM car_models;
SELECT year, model_name, manufacturer FROM car_models ORDER BY year DESC;
SELECT model_name, year, manufacturer FROM car_models WHERE manufacturer = 'Toyota';
SELECT id, engine_type, horsepower FROM engine_specs ORDER BY horsepower DESC;
SELECT * FROM car_models WHERE manufacturer = 'Toyota';
SELECT model_name, year FROM car_models WHERE year > 2010 ORDER BY year DESC;

SELECT cm.model_name, es.engine_type, fe.city_mpg FROM car_models cm JOIN engine_specs es ON cm.id = es.car_model_id JOIN fuel_efficiency fe ON cm.id = fe.car_model_id WHERE fe.city_mpg > 25 ORDER BY fe.city_mpg DESC;
SELECT em.car_model_id, em.co2_emissions, ft.fuel_type FROM emissions em JOIN fuel_types ft ON em.car_model_id = ft.id WHERE em.co2_emissions < 100 ORDER BY em.co2_emissions ASC;

SELECT cm.model_name, es.horsepower, em.nitrogen_oxides FROM car_models cm JOIN engine_specs es ON cm.id = es.car_model_id JOIN emissions em ON cm.id = em.car_model_id WHERE es.horsepower > 200 ORDER BY es.horsepower DESC;
